DR HORTON REALTY OF CENTRAL FLORIDA LLC

data.description: Looking for a place to call home, this is it. This beautiful two story home has a spacious open floor plan downstairs with a wonderful flow from kitchen to dining area to living room. Perfect for entertaining. Just off the entry hall from the front door is a half bath. The kitchen appliances are all Samsung stainless steel and complete the look with the shaker-style cabinets. The walk-in pantry is a delight for kitchen organization. The windows allow for natural light to brighten up the living space if desired with a backyard that leads to a water view. Upstairs the master bedroom has a tiled shower with dual vanities and a spacious walk-in closet. The other two bedrooms have a Jack and Jill bathroom with dual vanities as well.  The loft area provides an opportunity to have a separate game room, or additional living space.  Located within 10 miles from Legoland Resort and a quick drive to both Orlando and Tampa, this home is perfectly suited for being able to get access to Disney, Universal, Seaworld, and the beaches quickly. This beautiful home is a must see and won't last long.
